  <brief_title>Ultrasound-guided Axillary Artery vs Femoral Artery Cannulation.</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Study of Ultrasound-guided Axillary and Femoral Artery Cannulation in Mechanically Ventilated Critically Ill Patients.</official_title>
