  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main purpose of the study is to compare two ultrasound-guided arterial cannulation
      procedures: in-plane infraclavicular axillary artery cannulation and out-of-plane femoral
      artery cannulation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
